---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="About — WholeHearted" description="Meet Chris and Molly Broad — the hearts behind WholeHearted.live.">

  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden py-20 -mx-4 px-4">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 -z-10 bg-gradient-to-r from-rose/15 via-ivory via-50% to-sage/10"></div>
    <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <p class="text-sm font-medium text-wine uppercase tracking-wide mb-4">Our Story</p>
      <h1 class="brand-font text-4xl md:text-5xl font-medium tracking-tight text-ink">
        Meet the Broads
      </h1>
      <span class="mx-auto mt-4 block h-1.5 w-24 rounded-full bg-wine"></span>
      <p class="mt-6 max-w-xl text-base text-ink/70 mx-auto">
        A nutritionist, a pastoral counselor, a nurse, and a veteran — and most importantly, a wife and husband
        who believe you were made to feel whole.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Chris & Molly Together -->
  <section class="py-16 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <div class="rounded-2xl border border-ink/10 bg-white/70 p-8 md:p-12">
      <p class="text-rose font-semibold tracking-widest text-sm uppercase mb-4">Why We Started WholeHearted</p>
      <p class="text-ink/75 leading-relaxed mb-5 text-lg">
        WholeHearted didn't start as a business idea — it started as a conviction.
      </p>
      <p class="text-ink/70 leading-relaxed mb-5">
        Between us, we've spent decades in emergency medicine, military service, functional nutrition, and pastoral
        care. We've sat with people in their hardest moments — in the ER, in counseling rooms, in prayer. And
        over and over, we saw the same pattern: people suffering from conditions that were largely preventable,
        feeling unsupported, and not knowing where to turn.
      </p>
      <p class="text-ink/70 leading-relaxed mb-5">
        When we discovered the Feel Great System through Unicity, we didn't see a product — we saw a tool that
        aligned with everything we already believed about how the body was designed to work. We tried it ourselves.
        We saw real results. And we knew we had to share it.
      </p>
      <p class="text-ink/70 leading-relaxed">
        But more than sharing a product, we wanted to build something with a soul — a community where faith,
        science, and genuine care come together. That's WholeHearted. And we're glad you're here.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Meet Molly -->
  <section class="py-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 md:gap-12 items-start">

      <!-- Photo placeholder -->
      <div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden bg-ink/5 border border-ink/10 aspect-[4/5] flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center p-8">
        <!-- Replace this div with an <img> tag when you have a photo:
             <img src="/team/molly.jpg" alt="Molly Broad" class="w-full h-full object-cover object-top" />
        -->
        <div class="w-20 h-20 rounded-full bg-sage/20 flex items-center justify-center text-sage text-3xl mb-4">M</div>
        <p class="text-ink/40 text-sm">Photo coming soon</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Bio -->
      <div class="py-4">
        <p class="text-sage font-semibold tracking-widest text-sm uppercase mb-2">Co-Founder</p>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-ink tracking-tight mb-1">Molly Broad</h2>
        <p class="text-ink/50 text-sm mb-6">Functional Nutrition · Pastoral Counselor · BS Family & Child Studies</p>

        <p class="text-ink/70 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          Molly brings a rare combination of gifts to WholeHearted — the mind of a trained nutritionist, the
          heart of a pastoral counselor, and the grounding of a family systems scholar.
        </p>
        <p class="text-ink/70 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          Her training in functional nutrition means she understands not just what people should eat, but
          why their bodies respond the way they do — and how to support real, sustainable change from the inside out.
          She speaks the same scientific language as the Feel Great System.
        </p>
        <p class="text-ink/70 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          As a volunteer pastoral counselor at her church, Molly has walked alongside countless people through
          grief, transition, and healing. She knows that wellness is never just physical — it's emotional,
          relational, and deeply spiritual.
        </p>
        <p class="text-ink/70 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Her degree in Family and Child Studies shapes how she thinks about community — not as a network,
          but as a family. Everyone who joins WholeHearted is welcomed as one.
        </p>

        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
          {["Functional Nutrition", "Pastoral Counselor", "Family & Child Studies", "Community Builder"].map((tag) => (
            <span class="rounded-full bg-sage/15 text-sage text-xs font-medium px-3 py-1">{tag}</span>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Divider -->
  <div class="mx-auto my-4 h-px max-w-3xl bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-wine/20 to-transparent"></div>

  <!-- Meet Chris -->
  <section class="py-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 md:gap-12 items-start">

      <!-- Bio (left on desktop for Chris) -->
      <div class="py-4 md:order-1">
        <p class="text-rose font-semibold tracking-widest text-sm uppercase mb-2">Co-Founder</p>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-ink tracking-tight mb-1">Chris Broad</h2>
        <p class="text-ink/50 text-sm mb-6">Emergency Room RN · Retired U.S. Army Veteran</p>

        <p class="text-ink/70 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          Chris has spent his career on the front lines of human health. As an Emergency Room Registered Nurse,
          he's seen firsthand what happens when the body breaks down — and how often those crises could have
          been prevented with the right support, education, and tools.
        </p>
        <p class="text-ink/70 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          His years of service in the U.S. Army instilled in him a deep commitment to discipline, integrity,
          and showing up for others — values that run through everything WholeHearted does. He doesn't recommend
          anything he hasn't personally vetted, and he brings a clinician's eye to every conversation about health.
        </p>
        <p class="text-ink/70 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Chris believes the best healthcare is preventive care — and that a faith-centered community is one
          of the most powerful tools for lasting wellness.
        </p>

        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
          {["Emergency Room RN", "U.S. Army Veteran", "Metabolic Health Advocate", "Faith & Wellness"].map((tag) => (
            <span class="rounded-full bg-rose/10 text-rose text-xs font-medium px-3 py-1">{tag}</span>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Photo placeholder -->
      <div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden bg-ink/5 border border-ink/10 aspect-[4/5] flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center p-8 md:order-2">
        <!-- Replace this div with an <img> tag when you have a photo:
             <img src="/team/chris.jpg" alt="Chris Broad" class="w-full h-full object-cover object-top" />
        -->
        <div class="w-20 h-20 rounded-full bg-rose/20 flex items-center justify-center text-rose text-3xl mb-4">C</div>
        <p class="text-ink/40 text-sm">Photo coming soon</p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Brand ribbon divider -->
  <div class="mx-auto my-12 h-px max-w-3xl bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-wine/30 to-transparent"></div>

  <!-- Together — the WholeHearted difference -->
  <section class="py-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <div class="text-center mb-10">
      <p class="text-rose font-semibold tracking-widest text-sm uppercase mb-3">Why It Matters</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-ink tracking-tight">Body. Mind. Spirit.</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-ink/60 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Together, Chris and Molly bring credentials and calling that cover the whole person.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-3 gap-6 text-center">
      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-ink/10 bg-white/60 p-6">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-rose/15 flex items-center justify-center text-rose text-xl mx-auto mb-4">🩺</div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-ink mb-2">Body</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-ink/65 leading-relaxed">Chris's clinical background as an ER nurse and his functional knowledge of metabolic health means real, medically grounded guidance.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-ink/10 bg-white/60 p-6">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-sage/15 flex items-center justify-center text-sage text-xl mx-auto mb-4">🌿</div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-ink mb-2">Mind</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-ink/65 leading-relaxed">Molly's functional nutrition training and family systems education means she addresses the whole lifestyle — not just what's on your plate.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-ink/10 bg-white/60 p-6">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-gold/15 flex items-center justify-center text-gold text-xl mx-auto mb-4">🙏</div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-ink mb-2">Spirit</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-ink/65 leading-relaxed">Molly's pastoral counseling and their shared faith keeps this community rooted in what matters most — purpose, grace, and belonging.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Brand ribbon divider -->
  <div class="mx-auto my-12 h-px max-w-3xl bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-wine/30 to-transparent"></div>

  <!-- Values Section -->
  <section class="py-8">
    <div class="rounded-3xl bg-sage/15 py-16 px-8">
      <h2 class="brand-font text-2xl md:text-3xl font-medium text-ink text-center mb-12">
        What We Stand For
      </h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <div class="h-12 w-12 shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-rose/20 text-rose text-xl">♥</div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink mb-1">Faith First</h3>
            <p class="text-ink/70 text-sm">Everything we do is rooted in faith. We believe lasting wellness starts with a whole heart aligned with God's purpose.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <div class="h-12 w-12 shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-sage/25 text-sage text-xl">✓</div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink mb-1">Integrity Always</h3>
            <p class="text-ink/70 text-sm">No gimmicks, no hype. We share what works, recommend what we use, and tell the truth — even when it's not easy.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <div class="h-12 w-12 shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-gold/20 text-gold text-xl">✦</div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink mb-1">Education Over Sales</h3>
            <p class="text-ink/70 text-sm">We teach, we share, we answer questions. An informed community makes better choices — and that's the goal.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <div class="h-12 w-12 shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-rose/15 text-rose text-xl">❋</div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink mb-1">Real Community</h3>
            <p class="text-ink/70 text-sm">Not followers — family. We show up, we encourage, we celebrate wins together. This journey is better shared.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Scripture -->
  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto text-center">
      <div class="mx-auto my-8 h-px max-w-xs bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-wine/30 to-transparent"></div>
      <blockquote class="brand-font text-2xl md:text-3xl font-medium text-ink italic">
        "Love the Lord your God with all your heart and with all your soul and with all your strength."
      </blockquote>
      <p class="mt-4 text-ink/50 text-sm">Deuteronomy 6:5</p>
      <div class="mx-auto my-8 h-px max-w-xs bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-wine/30 to-transparent"></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="py-8 mb-8">
    <div class="rounded-3xl bg-sage/20 py-20 px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="brand-font text-2xl md:text-3xl font-medium text-ink mb-4">
        Ready to join the journey?
      </h2>
      <p class="text-ink/70 max-w-xl mx-auto mb-8">
        Whether you're curious about wellness, looking for community, or ready to dive in —
        we'd love to have you. Come as you are.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a
          href="/live"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-rose px-7 py-3 text-white font-semibold hover:bg-rose/85 transition"
        >
          Join a Live Session
        </a>
        <a
          href="/shop"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl border border-ink/30 px-7 py-3 text-ink hover:bg-ink/5 transition"
        >
          Explore the Feel Great System
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
